OL,4,CRacism probe as 'bananas thrown at
OL,5,CCardiff City academy players'
OL,6, The family of a child who said he faced
OL,7, racist bullying at Cardiff City academy
OL,8, have accused the club of not taking the
OL,9, allegations seriously enough.
OL,11,FThe boy, whose father is Arabian, said
OL,12,Fthe worst incident was having bananas
OL,13,Fthrown at him and a black friend on a
OL,14,Fyouth team minibus.
OL,16,FThe Football Association is understood
OL,17,Fto be probing discriminatory behaviour
OL,18,Fat the Championship club.
